Privacy Policy – Earn Your Screen

Last updated: 2025-03-01

Earn Your Screen (“the App”) helps you focus by locking distracting apps or your entire phone until you complete a short challenge.

1. Data we collect

1.1 Account data
If you choose to sign in with Google, we collect:
- Your Google account identifier (UID)
- Your name and email address
- Your Google profile photo (if available)

This data is provided by Google Sign-In and stored in Firebase Authentication.

1.2 App usage data
On your device, the App uses Android’s usage access permission to:
- Detect which app is currently in the foreground
- Detect when you open blocked apps

This information is processed locally on your device to decide when to show the lock screen. We do not send lists of your installed apps or foreground apps to our own servers.

1.3 Device information
We may collect basic technical information such as:
- App version
- Device model and OS version
This is used only for debugging and improving the App.

2. How we use your data

We use your data to:
- Authenticate you (Google Sign-In / Firebase Authentication)
- Enforce focus sessions (locking selected apps or full phone)
- Improve stability, fix bugs and understand how features are used (aggregated and anonymised where possible)

We do not sell your data.

3. Third-party services

The App uses:
- Google Sign-In
- Firebase Authentication

These services process your data in accordance with their own privacy policies:
- Google: https://policies.google.com/privacy
- Firebase: https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy

4. Data sharing

We do not share your personal data with third parties except:
- Service providers like Google/Firebase that help us run authentication and infrastructure
- When required by law

5. Data retention

We keep your account data for as long as your account is active. You can request deletion of your account data by contacting us at the email address below.

Most focus-session data (blocked apps, timers) is stored only on your device and is cleared when you uninstall the App or reset its data.

6. Children

Earn Your Screen is intended for users aged 13 and older. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe a child has provided us with personal information, please contact us so we can delete it.
